title: Bruckell Moonhawk Bluesmobile Skin
message:
Once again "It's 106 miles to Chicago we got a full tank of gas, half a pack of cigarettes, its dark and we're wearing sunglasses.. hit it!"

When you wreck your 4 door sedan in a cop chase and have to resort to a 2 door coupe the Bruckell Moonhawk is a fabulous choice.

This skin has two versions a "clean" version and a "dirty" version.

No other mods are required to make this work, but it wouldn't hurt to check out my other Bluesmobile mod here: [URL]https://www.beamng.com/resources/chevy-caprice-bluesmobile-skin.6905/[/URL]

[B]Installation[/B]
Manual Installation: Hit the Download Now button and drag the zip file into C:\Users\[YOUR USERNAME]\Documents\BeamNG.drive\mods.

Automatic Installation: Just hit the Subscribe button and it will download the files automatically through the game.

[B]PLEASE DO NOT RE UPLOAD THIS ANYWHERE
